 oral cladribine with immunosuppressive or myelosuppressive agents should be avoided if possible.', 'Major', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/33181/', '', 'Pertuzumab, Vismodegib, Ivosidenib, Belzutifan, Sonidegib, Mitotane, Porfimer sodium, Estramustine, Celecoxib, Aminolevulinic acid, Tazemetostat, More', 'Antithymocyte immunoglobulin (rabbit), Secukinumab, Anifrolumab, Ravulizumab, Mycophenolic acid, Tacrolimus, Abatacept, Apremilast, Inebilizumab, Belumosudil, Belimumab, More', 1767369485);
